    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You perceive the space between light and darkness, and draw power from it. Shadows conceal and protect you, while revealing the locations of those who dare to hide within them. Over time, you develop the ability to deny the warmth of light or life to your enemies.<br><br><strong>Phrenic Pool Ability:</strong> Wisdom<br><br><strong>Bonus Spells:</strong>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.h4hrop7rq2c9phyi]{Blurred Movement} (1st),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.advqdmonj6ro62u7]{Fear The Sun} (4th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.jdsvncnna6oy189a]{Deeper Darkness} (6th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.cmwcavfyc1vbehy8]{Shadow Step} (8th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.2q48ogrz3840xwi7]{Shadow Evocation} (10th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.btoow6tyv39443gh]{Shadow Walk} (12th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.8rf2ucrtzmxooyw6]{Lunar Veil} (14th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.h9dzj2fr5lksdjcp]{Umbral Strike} (16th),&nbsp;</li>\n<li>@Compendium[pf1.spells.0mt9mso6wdhfafpo]{Polar Midnight} (18th).</li>\n</ul>",
